---
title: HelloHero: Cheesy White Fish & Spiced Veggie Traybake with Chilli-Parsley Butter
description: This one-tray wonder combines fresh and tender white fish with a warming medley of colourful veggies, all enhanced by a tangy chilli parsley butter. Who knew something so healthy could taste so good?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
